SMS Engagement Filters

Here are some examples of common SMS engagement use cases.

SMS Engagement over a Period of Time

This filter looks for individuals who had at least two SMS engagements between May 1, 2020 and June 1, 2020.

EXAMPLE
SMS Engagement | Count | At Least | 2
Engagement Date Time | Is Between | 2020-05-01 AND 2020-06-01

Delivered SMS Messages

This filter looks for individuals who had an SMS delivered to their phone.

EXAMPLE
SMS Engagement | Count | At Least | 1
Engagement Channel Action | Is Equal To | Delivered

Keyword Text and Opt Ins

This filter finds individuals who opted in to the keyword text FreeGift in the next 30 days.

EXAMPLE
SMS Engagement | Count | At Least | 1
Engagement Channel Action | Is Equal To | Opt In
AND
Engagement Date Time | Next Number Of Days | 30
AND
Keyword Text | Is Equal To | FreeGift

Keyword Engagement in the Last 30 Days

This filter finds individuals who have engaged with the keyword EasterHunt! at least three times in the last 30 days.

EXAMPLE
SMS Engagement | Count | At Least | 3
Keyword Test | Is Equal To | EasterHunt!
AND
Engagement Date Time | Last Number of Days | 30

Keyword Engagement by Location

This filter finds individuals who have engaged with the keyword TreasureTruck!, have a postal code text of 734, and the city name of San Francisco or New York.

EXAMPLE
SMS Engagement | Count | At Least | 1
Keyword Text | Is Equal To | TreasureTruck!

AND

Contact Point Phone | Count | At Least | 1
Postal Code Text | Begins With | 734
AND
City Name | Is In | San Francisco, New York
